EDA OF THE ELECTRIC VEHICLE POPULATION

BACKGROUND DETAILS AROUND THE DATA

This dataset shows the Battery Electric Vehicles (BEVs) and Plug-in Hybrid Electric Vehicles (PHEVs) that are currently registered through Washington State Department of Licensing (DOL). State of Washington This dataset is intended for public access and use. Open Database License (ODbL)

4. What are the market shares of different electric vehicle types (e.g., battery electric, plug-in hybrid) in different regions?

By County

In[98]:
cond4 = year2023[year2023['County'].isin(Top5County)]
County_Type_counts = cond4.loc[:,['County', 'Electric Vehicle Type']].value_counts()
In[93]:
county_df = County_Type_counts.reset_index(name='Count')
counties = county_df['County'].unique()
fig,axes = plt.subplots(nrows=len(counties), ncols=1, figsize=(8, 5 * len(counties)))
for ax, county in zip(axes, counties):
    county_data = county_df[county_df['County'] == county]
    ax.pie(county_data['Count'], labels=county_data['Electric Vehicle Type'], autopct='%1.1f%%', startangle=90)
    ax.set_title(f'Electric Vehicle Types in {county}')
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
